data.description: 3 bed, 2 1/2 bath open concept 1713 sq.ft.  over-the-top remodeled brick open concept craftsman on 6.7 town lots.  Located in the same neighborhood as all the schools.  This home has it all.  Custom built kitchen cabinets with new appliances and lots of counter space.  There is a large laundry room tucked behind the kitchen along the hallway.  Luxury vinyl plank floors throughout.  Drywalled first floor with whitewashed shiplap walls and ceilings upstairs.  Extra-large master suite on the main floor is separated from the main living area.  Also, there is a half bath in the hallway behind the main living area.  2nd floor has two bedrooms, a newly added large full bath, and an open space around the stairway which would be perfect for a computer/study area.  New heat pump, new windows and doors, new metal roof.  New pex plumbing, new wiring.  There is a full unfinished dry basement with access from interior or exterior.  Life-time warranty basement dry system installed.  Workshop in well-lit basement along with lots of storage.  Workshop in outbuilding was being used as a she shed for crafts.   The large back yard has a stone-lined koi pond with waterfall.  There are large concrete pads in front and one side which provide lots of parking for RVs or guests.  The only thing this home needs is a new family!  Shown only to prequalified buyers.
